<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sign In - NextBid Portal</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #1e3a5f 50%, #111827 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .container { width: 100%; max-width: 900px; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-out; }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .logo-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .logo-img { width: 200px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto 16px; display: block; }
    .logo-section p { color: #9ca3af; font-size: 16px; }
    .split-card {
      display: flex;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .left-column { flex: 1; padding: 40px; border-right: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .right-column { flex: 1; padding: 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f1f5f9 100%); }
    .left-column h2 { color: #111827; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .error {
      background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; color: #b91c1c;
      padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 16px; }
    label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #374151; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; }
    input[type="email"], input[type="password"] {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; transition: all 0.2s; background: #fff;
    }
    input:focus { outline: none; border-color: #3b82f6; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); }
    input::placeholder { color: #9ca3af; }
    button[type="submit"] {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px; background: #2563eb; color: #fff;
      border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; margin-top: 8px;
    }
    button[type="submit"]:hover { background: #1d4ed8; }
    .workspace-msg { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
    .register-link {
      text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .register-link a { color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .register-link a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .right-column h3 { color: #111827; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .right-column .tagline { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .feature-list { list-style: none; }
    .feature-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-right: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 20px;
    }
    .feature-icon.blue { background: #dbeafe; }
    .feature-icon.purple { background: #ede9fe; }
    .feature-icon.green { background: #dcfce7; }
    .feature-icon.orange { background: #ffedd5; }
    .feature-content h4 { color: #111827; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .feature-content p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 24px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 14px; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .split-card { flex-direction: column; }
      .left-column { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo-section">
      <img src="/images/nextbid-logo.png" alt="NextBid" class="logo-img">
      <p>Government Contract Intelligence</p>
    </div>
    <div class="split-card">
      <div class="left-column">
        <h2>Sign In</h2>
        <% if (error) { %><div class="error"><%= error %></div><% } %>
        <form method="POST" action="/login">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required placeholder="you@company.com">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="password">Password</label>
            <input type="password" id="password" name="password" autocomplete="current-password" required placeholder="••••••••">
          </div>
          <button type="submit">Sign In</button>
        </form>
        <p class="workspace-msg">You'll be taken to your workspace</p>
        <div class="register-link">Don't have an account? <a href="/register">Create one</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="right-column">
        <h3>What You Get</h3>
        <p class="tagline">Everything you need to win government contracts</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon blue">&#128269;</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Real-Time Opportunity Discovery</h4>
              <p>Automatically find relevant bid opportunities across 20+ government sources the moment they're posted.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon purple">&#129302;</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>AI-Powered Scope Analysis</h4>
              <p>Our AI reads and analyzes every solicitation, extracting key requirements so you know exactly what's needed.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon green">&#128196;</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Automated Proposal Generation</h4>
              <p>Generate tailored proposal drafts in minutes, not days. Let AI handle the heavy lifting.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon orange">&#127919;</div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h4>Smart Match Scoring</h4>
              <p>See at a glance which opportunities are the best fit for your company with our intelligent scoring system.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer"><p>&copy; 2025 NextBid. All rights reserved.</p></div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
